      • driveAction

        public void driveAction(double left,
                        double right)
        Sets the motor controllers to run using the percent output mode
        Parameters:
        left - A value between -1 and 1. Typically a value from the controller's left joystick is passed here
        right - A value between -1 and 1. Typically a value from the controller's right joystick is passed here

      • driveVelocity

        public void driveVelocity(double left,
                          double right)
        Sets the motor controllers to run using the velocity output mode. Left and Right parameters are used as scaling factors.
        Parameters:
        left - A value between -1 and 1. Typically a value from the controller's left joystick is passed here
        right - A value between -1 and 1. Typically a value from the controller's right joystick is passed here
